OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771963515
OL,3,CBus drivers continue 10-day walkout on
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Man
OL,6,FBus drivers on the Isle of Man will
OL,7,Fcontinue their ten-day walkout, in a
OL,8,Fdispute over pay and working
OL,9,Fconditions.
OL,11,FIt comes after union representatives
OL,12,Fand with officers from the Department
OL,13,Fof Infrastructure failed to reach an
OL,14,Fagreement this afternoon.
OL,16,FRegional Officer for Unite the Union,
OL,17,FDebbie Halsall, says the union
OL,18,Frepresents '99.9%' of bus drivers on
OL,19,Fthe island.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
