OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771963515
OL,3,CBus drivers continue 10-day walkout on
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Man
OL,6,FThey added that the department 'has
OL,7,Fmade six pay offers to try to settle
OL,8,Fthe dispute'.
OL,10,FThe statement concluded by saying:
OL,11,F'The Department cannot give a running
OL,12,Fcommentary on the negotiations but it
OL,13,Fremains fully committed to engaging
OL,14,Fwith Unite at any time on proposals
OL,15,Fthat could form an acceptable and
OL,16,Faffordable settlement.'
OL,18,FNegotiations are set to continue with
OL,19,Fthe assistance of the Manx Industrial
OL,20,FRelations Service.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
